userPromptTemplate:
Analyze {symbol} trading data:

Current Price: {price}
Price Change 24h: {priceChange} ({priceChangePercent}%)
24h High: {highPrice} | 24h Low: {lowPrice}
24h Volume: {volume} {baseAsset}

Order Book Summary:
- Top 5 Bids: {topBids}
- Top 5 Asks: {topAsks}
- Bid/Ask Spread: {spread}

Recent Trades (last 10):
{recentTrades}

Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "symbol": "{symbol}",
  "timestamp": <unix ms>,
  "trend": "BULLISH" | "BEARISH" | "NEUTRAL",
  "signal": {
    "action": "BUY" | "SELL" | "HOLD",
    "strength": "STRONG" | "MODERATE" | "WEAK",
    "confidence": <0-100>,
    "entryPrice": "<price or null>",
    "takeProfit": "<price or null>",
    "stopLoss": "<price or null>",
    "reasoning": "<2-3 sentence reasoning>"
  },
  "summary": "<2-3 sentence market summary>",
  "keyLevels": {
    "support": ["<price1>", "<price2>"],
    "resistance": ["<price1>", "<price2>"]
  },
  "indicators": [
    { "name": "Volume", "value": "<value>", "interpretation": "<brief>" },
    { "name": "Spread", "value": "<value>", "interpretation": "<brief>" },
    { "name": "Order Flow", "value": "<Buy/Sell>", "interpretation": "<brief>" }
  ]
}
